'''黑素皮质素受体1''' ('''MC1R''')是一种[[G蛋白耦合受体|G蛋白耦合受体]]，长度约为310个[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]左右，其[[基因序列|基因序列]]只有一个[[外显子|外显子]], 有7个[[跨膜结构域|跨膜结构域]], 是最小的G蛋白耦合受体<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ren |first1=Gang |last2=Li |first2=En |last3=Zhao |first3=Shiye |last4=Jiang |first4=Yanqiong |last5=Wang |first5=Shasha |last6=Tang |first6=Sixian |last7=Hu |first7=Huijian |title=Correlation between color polymorphism and the MC1R gene of Lanius schach |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-06-20 |volume=28 |issue=6 |pages=688 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019307}}</ref>。

